r:#ffffff;\">다만 총 디자인된 pdf를 다운로드 받는 버튼등의 기능을 만들지는 기획 마무리 단계에서 결정합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-531519df-d92e-4d2b-a6e7-92b0855aed28\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7997224c-3c3e-452b-a24d-54330b868f97\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">작성자의 의도는 디자인된 페이지 하나 하나를 쪼개서 이미지 파일로 올리는 것을 고려해 기획하고 있습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ce938fe-dbbf-412e-839e-dca29d9805c5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a5ab422b-0345-43af-a731-212ae705fdba\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b37e6c2-77c8-4614-a363-db856a10d886\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7b37e6c2-77c8-4614-a363-db856a10d886\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfMjIz/MDAxNjY0MjUyMjY3NDAw.vKkoYHFfi9Rxr7shGU4URlHz0v1XoOYt5xfn1je0178g.-Eug3YNbb6erLWEFa0NWzeiTN3XR9qRqyNHiXKMokWkg.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"37\", \"originalHeight\" : \"37\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfMjIz/MDAxNjY0MjUyMjY3NDAw.vKkoYHFfi9Rxr7shGU4URlHz0v1XoOYt5xfn1je0178g.-Eug3YNbb6erLWEFa0NWzeiTN3XR9qRqyNHiXKMokWkg.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a8351c66-a46f-449d-ae84-75c7be7420f2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a71a5c95-ef84-4cc7-a852-322238c8181a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7c7f2a7d-9552-44d7-96a9-7d247fc99e65\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>기타 요청사항​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e3620fbe-1310-4099-952e-ee40914d8d02\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5ef0b1ab-5253-4ea9-9ed1-67ccb2000a86\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 부분은 주문자가 요청사항이 따로 있을 때 텍스트나 이미지를 업로드해서 올리는것을 말합니다. 이 부분은 텍스트 제한 수나 이미지 용량을 고려해서 작업해야하며 이 요청사항을 한눈에 확인하고 관리자가 알람으로 인지할 수 있는 기능을 만들면 좋습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-adc72c73-8183-401a-9dde-74dc4b4fd12a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-72f091f7-e00a-44cd-9f4a-d3d664c470f3\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">요청사항을 확인하고 그 요청사항대로 디자인을 하며 예를들어 교정과 커뮤니케이션 방법을 추가로 고려할 수 있습니다. 이 말은 카카오톡, 채팅봇이나 기타 문자서비스 기능을 의미합니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a64d4a37-1cf5-4147-862e-834d882b0e79\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1cb86197-eeed-4d9c-a0ff-8085d4d6896d\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e747567b-ec40-4af2-ac2b-f413debe6f12\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e747567b-ec40-4af2-ac2b-f413debe6f12\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfMjc4/MDAxNjY0MjUyNDgwNTUw.VD4DXWs7yyZ61muPAQtNDzKKwUHwRt30l4cZ1S5Lp8gg.OCOPAY10JyeG-DMjw_NjfVUc5TddIeYg-Mm4JCyP4t0g.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"37\", \"originalHeight\" : \"37\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfMjc4/MDAxNjY0MjUyNDgwNTUw.VD4DXWs7yyZ61muPAQtNDzKKwUHwRt30l4cZ1S5Lp8gg.OCOPAY10JyeG-DMjw_NjfVUc5TddIeYg-Mm4JCyP4t0g.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3ee4021b-134d-4d4d-a745-46eed447a0c4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-93c2a2cd-041b-4d91-a932-dfc54fc799c6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-730c4ec0-ca30-49e5-8bf7-3d9703f68c40\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>종이 변경</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2638793d-c396-4caf-8aa7-7cfe3c822d65\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5f9bc01e-aeb7-455b-a7e7-7666c2c49737\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">주문시 종이를 변경할 수 있습니다. 종이 변경에 따른 가격표시는 바뀔 수 있습니다. 서두에서 말했듯이 (주)파파스컴퍼니 홈페이지는 가격노출 주문형 사이트가 아닙니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1c3c294f-650f-4cbf-92ff-7e97047a8120\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c12a097d-8932-43f9-a78a-4a4ea1a9b271\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">종이 변경에 따른 비용 추가는 일부 계산으로 보여줄 수도 있고 안될 수도 있습니다. 8번 사항입니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-024c443c-1038-4b34-b3a4-20752858ef3c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-805a6239-3c6f-475f-b55e-0b051cd48f84\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6d5f68fa-72d1-426c-bb2a-f62d240c6ef2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6d5f68fa-72d1-426c-bb2a-f62d240c6ef2\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfNiAg/MDAxNjY0MjUyODM4ODE1.vPIJeWIFGsKtxBrx1QMAnHknCGYUamy86LkLa2um77Ag.4OIQ71KKxbD6VF2diudKkmlMdCg4hTVYr9ajZc0bWpcg.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"37\", \"originalHeight\" : \"37\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfNiAg/MDAxNjY0MjUyODM4ODE1.vPIJeWIFGsKtxBrx1QMAnHknCGYUamy86LkLa2um77Ag.4OIQ71KKxbD6VF2diudKkmlMdCg4hTVYr9ajZc0bWpcg.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ceff7f32-d329-47d0-9f94-02aba0054812\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-34b6f9a1-998d-4e2f-915e-61085fba5478\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c9cd80d8-8b91-4928-a50b-e1325b4a2c4b\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>페이지 선택​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-10948f27-f6d4-4ea6-b21f-58c0c7b19960\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-94ba79dd-aca8-436c-988a-b8f7760f482e\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">주문자는 기본 36page 상품을 20page등으로 수정해 주문할 수 있습니다. 이때 예상가격은 상담 후 노출, 또는 견적서 요청으로 표시하거나 노출을 금지할 수 도 있습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e9fe7b59-9142-43c7-bc3a-d10d554520c4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-01f09303-a4e5-4d43-be1a-c756ef139b2c\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">가장 민감한 가격 노출 부분은 기획단께에서 추후 결정하겠습니다. </span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1a208fc7-08fd-419c-aa94-99e7dabff251\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f8999719-8f83-4cac-9c94-d5df82e15829\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-be4fbcbd-9cf9-4933-948f-a6328f7ba106\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-be4fbcbd-9cf9-4933-948f-a6328f7ba106\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfNzUg/MDAxNjY0MjUyOTYwOTQy.hYG6iQWFWN0Z1ZxympJdr9lY4EN7Qad0gM4fJFm_JmIg.OL3pigRze-QTUyVaGmbRKkgcUKlRxI0gozefMHDDITQg.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"37\", \"originalHeight\" : \"37\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfNzUg/MDAxNjY0MjUyOTYwOTQy.hYG6iQWFWN0Z1ZxympJdr9lY4EN7Qad0gM4fJFm_JmIg.OL3pigRze-QTUyVaGmbRKkgcUKlRxI0gozefMHDDITQg.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7a4c469a-a709-4947-98d9-c433120c9269\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-91a92eac-8122-4ed2-b23d-e6882a35965c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e7f410b9-9ab7-40a7-857a-6694a48045d0\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>수량 선택​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ae88fe6c-2ddf-407e-8cfb-b70172e567fd\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-34a93df4-e382-41bf-81f6-554225eb585c\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">수량은 변경될 수 있습니다. 기본 수량을 Select Box로 선택할 수 있고 기타에서 텍스트를 입력할 수 있습니다. 입력시애는 Text Box로 변경됩니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b7bde2a4-32c8-4074-92c3-5507c684f8ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-406579ae-7698-4aca-ab51-e14aa4d1f481\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3ef6a84-186f-441d-9069-de14df7c1c23\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d3ef6a84-186f-441d-9069-de14df7c1c23\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfMTU0/MDAxNjY0MjUzMTI4NDY1.3-p7-K1hsnDSzfOE92s1pY25gChQKKl2KcR9N0f4d_sg.CtZ9XDaOb3yv3XHg4LDTjgAyJnL1hnk_JWUtLH6130sg.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"37\", \"originalHeight\" : \"37\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfMTU0/MDAxNjY0MjUzMTI4NDY1.3-p7-K1hsnDSzfOE92s1pY25gChQKKl2KcR9N0f4d_sg.CtZ9XDaOb3yv3XHg4LDTjgAyJnL1hnk_JWUtLH6130sg.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c2987b1-afcb-4de3-8355-8e23cf6a9fc2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dbed1a03-1fe1-48e6-ac10-e9575c87c051\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5e689939-9cc1-41ca-986e-458a2e40d0a5\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>예상 견적금액​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-458a3725-fbd1-4024-9f61-3933c2ec4fa7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f7d44e86-7fde-4619-b707-9a73bb03b654\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">예상 견적금액은 기본적은 템플릿으로 책정된 금액입니다. 종이나 수량 등이 변경된다면 안내를 통해 변경된 가격을 고지하거나 아니면 가격이 변동되었다고 주문자에게 전달할 수 있습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c0703651-cdc7-41f7-a45a-1d61de73e60a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-01c4f6c4-7be1-4d12-b048-165fcf8bab50\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">다시 말하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 가격 노출형 주문사이트가 아닙니다. 예상 금액만 어바웃으로 알려주고 디자인이나 주문 변경에 따라 가격이 변경될 수 있다고 고지하는 정도입니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b839455f-42b0-4704-af5c-ed01d70d6c43\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c4389789-cd6f-4f3c-93ea-37882629916e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca6c639b-1f6b-4f77-b78a-bf62839c59d3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ca6c639b-1f6b-4f77-b78a-bf62839c59d3\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfNzYg/MDAxNjY0MjUzMzA3MjYw.s9q-x2O07bPB_EJnKLvsMO52mefnu9c9rj-Y32w_IYgg.rgyS8JY2e40fnXuXPdzArfZUceeoCnVx05BYLMvRsFog.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"37\", \"originalHeight\" : \"37\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA5MjdfNzYg/MDAxNjY0MjUzMzA3MjYw.s9q-x2O07bPB_EJnKLvsMO52mefnu9c9rj-Y32w_IYgg.rgyS8JY2e40fnXuXPdzArfZUceeoCnVx05BYLMvRsFog.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8_%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8_%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80(2022-09-26).png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-667ad473-c4a6-493e-8d39-3e02405f151c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bd259f7b-bcc5-4172-afe1-a97de31aa42e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d6a2d53a-05fa-4e4e-a967-5436dfbd69b9\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>주문 및 교정</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-557f2b30-d454-48a4-86b8-0a5b66d35803\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-15208124-b18a-4335-9d9a-01d9bee96b54\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">주문페이지를 완성한겁니다. 우리는 이 정보로 가격을 메기고 견적서를 제출하며 고객과 커뮤니케이션 할것입니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-39543989-7f6e-4725-8879-403e5724ed19\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ba815842-e75e-4cda-b730-4de22c331521\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c3a0e864-5565-447e-a658-f5576918e7e4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-352d2a22-7851-4a05-b3e0-642ba2c36d57\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-440af445-56a6-4247-90f4-86a1a7f69d28\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1ad3114d-521b-432c-8a2e-6d2eb1b1864c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-569425d1-ff0f-4316-8b34-08659f5e2d64\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>다음 글의 내용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2ba59c0f-e402-4d09-a6c1-b9bafeb4fb00\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4b110d99-8a18-467d-89e1-c698e97e426e\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2a539d73-6b17-413a-8598-79640cadba5a\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[기획] 주문 엑셀 페이지 보강작업 및 수토리보드를 위한 PPT준비​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3779f4d6-f16e-490b-a18c-3848c83ea4bd\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-73236a19-a6fc-4a93-b7f0-77d8a05ddacd\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9abf85c7-2944-470f-9c03-0297302f26d5\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-aa7d48dd-58ea-4b97-82ef-c5d46ca1b36d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">문서를 다시 보강하는 작업을 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f7335442-17fb-4856-80c8-18a7ed37b779\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b0c27c58-d947-4ecc-8d08-26b56984ab14\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7457f9fa-b0d1-4a06-9a3e-8194a5a81d88\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7457f9fa-b0d1-4a06-9a3e-8194a5a81d88\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMDFfOTUg/MDAxNjY0NjE2ODIxNTQy.mkweT--20pg9uu8wp57nwPituD1D-GfozyZVVtYevNQg.wARhdgnBLhqaNbAfZIUv3owiUNdgD1ucA2ZQYaIddFYg.PNG.cookthede